# Install ReText Markdown Editor on Crostini on ChromeOS (Chromebook)

sudo apt install -y pip
sudo apt install -y python3-pip
pip install ReText
sudo pip install ReText
sudo apt install -y retext

All done. It is launchable from the Terminal with the command retext
It will appear in the Start Menu after some time, which allows you to pin it to the shelf.

It may require a PC restart to have it appear in the start menu, if it does not.

